data.description: Welcome to your new home! Spacious floor plan with 1500sf of living space. 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, plus Bonus Room! Open floor plan, updated features and finishes. SS appliances, farm sink, island, upgraded lighting package and 5 piece master bath. Oversized cedar decks for entertaining/BBQ. 10x12 storage shed. Private gated salt water boat launch.Sitting on a 1/4 acre lot located in the lovely quiet Timberlakes community which boasts 6 parks & 2 private lakes with fish. Kayaking, tubing, water skiing and motor boats are allowed. Parks include baseball field and dog park. Community center that host private events for residents. Don't miss out on this great property. Schedule today!
